<dl id="n42001c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42001c">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42001c"> 1(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> daughters &amp; / wives of D &mdash;</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">As for us, daughters and wives of Montreal, who have known by experience the filth of the confessional, we cannot sufficiently bless God for having shown us the error of our ways in teaching us that it is not at the feet of a man as weak and sinful as ourselves but at the feet of Christ alone, that we must seek salvation. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) xii</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
